<thisCommand> [<nick>|<-|+nick!user@host>]

Will add or remove a nick!user@host to/from your block list, limiting who can /msg you directly.

If no nick!user@host is specified, all blocks are listed.

All blocks are cleared upon disconnection.

Example(s):
---------------
/<thisCommand>
/<thisCommand> +Bob!*@*
/<thisCommand> -Alice!*@*
